  <div class="py-16">
    {/* Section Header */}
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Build Resilience</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-base-content/80">
        Entrepreneurial resilience is the non-negotiable survival skill for
        business. Success hinges on your mental fortitudeâ€”the ability to absorb
        the inevitable rejection and failure, learn, and persistently move
        forward. Overcome mental blocks through these real-world challenges
        designed to rewire your response to fear and distraction, forging the
        resilience required for success.
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Three Core Challenges */}
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
      {/* Challenge 1 - Feedback Seeker */}
      <div
        class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-base-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all relative"
      >
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:message-processing-outline" class="text-xl text-primary" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Feedback Seeker Challenge</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/80 ">
          Ask 5 people for honest feedback on an idea/product to embrace
          constructive criticism.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Challenge 2 - Stranger High-Five */}
      <div
        class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-base-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all relative"
      >
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:eye-outline" class="text-xl text-primary" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Stranger High-Five Challenge</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/80 mb-10">
          Ask 10 strangers for a high-five or fist bump to reduce social anxiety
          and build confidence.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Challenge 3 - Upsell Me */}
      <div
        class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-base-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all relative"
      >
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
        >
          <Icon name="mdi:hand-coin-outline"  class="text-xl text-primary" />
          
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Upsell Me Challenge</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/80 mb-10">
          Say 'no' to first offers in 3 stores to observe sales tactics and
          handle objections.
        </p>
    </div>

    {/* Free Challenge CTA */}
    <div
      class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/5 to-primary/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
    >
      <div class="text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
          Try a Free Challenge Today
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-base-content/80 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Experience our unique approach with a sample challenge designed to
          push your comfort zone in under 30 minutes.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary px-8">
            Start Free Challenge
          </a>
          <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn btn-ghost border-base-content/20">
            How Challenges Work
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>